Some notes before you proceed:

 · Make sure you're on the latest stable version of Magisk. This won't work if you're on some other half-assed root solution;
 · Make sure the file isn't bigger than 256Mb;
 · If you're flashing a ZIP that wipes/replaces /system or /vendor in any way… well thar be dragons, and I don't think you should proceed for safety reasons
